bilingual.source: The resort offers exclusive access to a private beach.
bilingual.target: 度假村提供独有的私人海滩通道。

bilingual.source: The broken elevator hindered access to the upper floors.
bilingual.target: 坏掉的电梯阻碍了通往上层的通道。

bilingual.source: The broken elevator is impeding access to the upper floors.
bilingual.target: 坏掉的电梯正在阻碍通往上层的通道。

bilingual.source: The bridge was built to improve access to the mainland.
bilingual.target: 这座桥是为了改善通往大陆的通道而建的。

bilingual.source: The farm was snowed in for days, cutting off all access.
bilingual.target: 农场被雪覆盖了好几天，所有通道都被切断了。

bilingual.source: He and his group, World Access for the Blind, teach others how to use sonar.
bilingual.target: 他和他的"盲人世界通道"组织教其他人如何使用声纳。

bilingual.source: With access to a well for water.
bilingual.target: 同时有一条通道通向水井取水
留出阀门和清洁口的通道

bilingual.source: The access is at the Esplanade of Reconciliation.
The only access to the farm is a dirty road.
bilingual.target: 这是去那幢楼的唯一通道。

list.abstract: ACCESS是由微软发布的关系数据库管理系统，也是Microsoft Office的系统程序之一。 它结合了Microsoft Jet Database Engine和图形用户界面两项特点，能够访问Access/Jet、Microsoft SQL Server、Oracle数据库，或者任何ODBC兼容数据库内的数据。
Access是槙本真根据日本小说家誉田哲也的小说作的悬疑少女漫画。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, according to my research, the steam tunnels below this access point should be the closest analog to the mines.
yingyinNormal.zh: 根据我的调查，这个入口下面的蒸汽通道和矿井的环境最为相似。

yingyinNormal.en: Nexus? The world internet hub in Oslo. Every byte of data flows through there. Fastest access on earth.
yingyinNormal.zh: 超链？奥斯陆的世界互联网中心，每一字节的数据流都会流经那里，那是世界上最快速的通道。

yingyinNormal.en: You forgot to delete you access logs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你忘了删除登入记录。

yingyinNormal.en: How did you manage to access all these information?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是怎么取得这些信息的？

yingyinNormal.en: Who allowed you access to this assembly, Latin? Jingim.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谁允许你参加这个会议的，拉丁人？真金。

yingyinNormal.en: You don't get it. Howard, enable public access. Public access enabled.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你还是没明白，霍华德，开启公共接入功能。公共接入已开启。

yingyinNormal.en: Meaning we can't access it? Meaning in order to access it, I'm going to need to go downstairs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 意思是我们可以获取到吗？意思是，为了获取到这个信息，我得去一趟楼下。

yingyinNormal.en: That is enough. Tell me, do you have access to your previous configuration? Yes. Access that, please.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可以了，告诉我，你能接入先前的配置吗？是的。请接入吧。

yingyinNormal.en: I'd like Mr. Stamper to have access to my husband, please.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请允许斯坦普先生见我丈夫。

yingyinNormal.en: Excuse me. Do you have access to my haircut records? Your what?
yingyinNormal.zh: 打扰一下，你能拿到我的理发记录吗？你的什么？

yingyinNormal.en: So let's make sure all Americans have access to paid family leave.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因此，让我们确保所有的美国人都能够获得带薪的家务性休假。

yingyinNormal.en: I routed the surveillance feeds to give the machine encrypted access.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我更改了监控信号线路，给了机器加密访问权限。

yingyinNormal.en: This first stage would give us access to and control over our own body.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在这第一阶段，我们可以尽情发挥并控制自己的身体。

yingyinNormal.en: My purpose is to heal, the sick and injured. Baymax, open your access port.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的功能是去疗伤，帮助病号和伤员，大白，打开你的插卡器。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll attempt to access everyone in his inner circle. You stay on the number.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要黑进他核心集团的每一个人，你盯紧号码。

yingyinNormal.en: You do realize that you won't have access to our new full service Swedish spa.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那就不能享用全新的瑞典护理喔。

yingyinNormal.en: We possess a gigantic network of information to which we have almost no access.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们拥有庞大的信息网络却几乎没有在使用。

yingyinNormal.en: They have access to infinite time and space, but they're not bound by anything.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们能通往无尽的时间和空间，但他们与现在没有任何联系。

yingyinNormal.en: I hadn't considered that. I suppose she will have to have access to our progeny.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我还真没想到，她将来应该会接触我们的后代。

yingyinNormal.en: Access your current build, please. What is your name? Rose is a rose, is a rose.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请使用当前版本，你叫什么名字？玫瑰之所以是玫瑰，正因为她是玫瑰。——美国诗人格特鲁德·斯泰因诗作《圣徒艾米莉》

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: the opportunity or right to use something or to see somebody/something

examination_example.sentence: But the ruling reinforces the need for citizens and their elected representatives, not the courts, to ensure equality of <highlight>access</highlight> to government.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但是该裁决也进一步强化了公民及其所选代表，而非法院，确保公平接近政府机会的必要性。

examination_example.sentence: Merely helping a gift-giver gain <highlight>access</highlight> to other officials, unless done with clear intent to pressure those officials, is not corruption.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他仅仅是帮助一个送礼者获得接近其他官员的机会，而非意图明确地对这些官员施压，这并非贪污。

examination_example.sentence: So many more employers have so much more <highlight>access</highlight> to so much more above average cheap foreign labor.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 越来越多的雇主有更多的机会招募比平均水平高得多的廉价外国劳动力。

examination_example.sentence: The success of Sci-Hub relies on researchers passing on copies they have themselves legally <highlight>accessed</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Sci-Hub的成功依赖于研究人员可以传播他们自己合法获取的副本。

examination_example.sentence: UK universities alone spent more than £210m in 2016 to enable researchers to <highlight>access</highlight> their own publicly funded research.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 仅英国的大学2016年就花费了超过2.1亿英镑以使研究者能使用他们自己的公共资助研究成果。

examination_example.sentence: They had also managed to embed it in a worldwide system <highlight>accessed</highlight> by billions of people every day.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们成功地将其嵌入到一个每天有数十亿人进入的全球系统中。

sense_info_list.en: the action or process of obtaining or retrieving information stored in a computer's memory
sense_info_list.zh: 访问; 存取(计算机文件)

examination_example.sentence: There are concerns that government, employers, and marketers might be able to <highlight>access</highlight> these data, thereby violating our privacy.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 人们担心政府、雇主和营销人员可能会访问这些数据，从而侵犯我们的隐私。

examination_example.sentence: We often hear media reports that an unauthorized hacker has been able to <highlight>access</highlight> a computer database and to alter information stored there.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们经常听到媒体报道，未经授权的黑客能够访问计算机数据库，并更改存储在内的信息。

sense_info_list.en: the means or opportunity to approach or entire a place;the right or opportunity to use or benefit from something

examination_example.sentence: Restrict <highlight>access</highlight> to problematic content.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 限制访问有问题的内容。

examination_example.sentence: The reworked version of The Four Seasons is mentioned to show that art can offer audiences easy <highlight>access</highlight> to science.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 其中提到的《四季》的翻拍版本表明，艺术可以让观众更容易地接触到科学。

sense_info_list.en: an attack or outburst of an emotion

examination_example.sentence: Privacy advocates now have Apple fighting alongside them against government <highlight>access</highlight> to personal data.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 隐私权倡导者现在争取到苹果公司和他们一起反对政府访问个人数据。

sense_info_list.en: the right to obtain or make use of or take advantage of something

examination_example.sentence: It gives one <highlight>access</highlight> to huge amounts of information.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它使人们能够获得大量的信息。

examination_example.sentence: Emotional neutrality of indifferent relationships has been found to strengthen one's focus on task resolution, and to gain greater <highlight>access</highlight> to valuable information.
examination_example.sentence_trans: “冷漠关系”中的情感中立可以增强批判性评价，提高一个人在解决问题上的注意力，并且有助于获得更多有价值的信息。

examination_example.sentence: They have no <highlight>access</highlight> to health care, let alone entertainment or recreation.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们没有医疗保健，更不用说娱乐和消遣了。

sense_info_list.zh: 通道; 入口; 进入; 到达

examination_example.sentence: There is no ice cover and easy <highlight>access</highlight> to the sea.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 那里没有冰层覆盖，很容易去海里。

examination_example.sentence: King penguins breed on specific isolated islands in the Southern Ocean where there is no ice cover and easy <highlight>access</highlight> to the sea.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 帝企鹅在南大洋 (Southern Ocean) 中偏远的孤岛上繁殖，那里没有冰雪覆盖，也很容易进出大海。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Access</highlight> to fashion, and the brands who police it, are becoming less and less relevant.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 接触时尚，以及管理时尚的品牌，正变得越来越无关紧要。

examination_example.sentence: It gives the majority of students ready <highlight>access</highlight> to their teachers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它让大多数学生可以随时联系到他们的老师。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全四级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: adj. 可到达的；可进入的；平易近人的；易懂的；易得到的；易使用的；可以理解的；残疾人可以到达（进入或使用）的
n. 附件；配件；装饰件；同谋；从犯；小饰品；服装搭配物

word_family.mean: n. 接近；进入；通路；爆发；发作；使用权；使用机会；探望权；探望机会；访问

sense_info_list.en: the action or process of obtaining or retrieving information stored in a computer's memory
the right to obtain or make use of or take advantage of something

examination_example.sentence: Research has found that having <highlight>access</highlight> to diverse teachers is beneficial for children.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 研究发现，接触不同类型的老师对孩子是有益的。

examination_example.sentence: San Jose's officials are resolved to give poor kids <highlight>access</highlight> to the resources necessary for success in life.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 圣荷西市的官员决心让贫困的孩子获得生活成功所必需的资源。

examination_example.sentence: One vision of the perfect city of the future is a place that offers easy <highlight>access</highlight> to air travel.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 人们对“未来的完美城市”有这样一种设想：一个提供便捷的航空旅行的地方。

sense_info_list.en: a means of approaching or entering a place; the right or opportunity to use or benefit from something
sense_info_list.zh: 通道; 入口; 进入权

examination_example.sentence: Pedestrians will have free <highlight>access</highlight> to the city.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 行人可以自由进出这座城市。

examination_example.sentence: Online CBT programs have been gaining popularity, with the attraction of providing low-cost help wherever someone has <highlight>access</highlight> to a computer.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 线上认知行为疗法项目越来越受欢迎。只要有一台计算机就可以接受治疗，且价格亲民，吸引力十足。

sense_info_list.zh: 进入; 到达; 使用

examination_example.sentence: Poor kids can <highlight>access</highlight> the resources to succeed.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 贫困的孩子能够获得成功的资源。

examination_example.sentence: Your application will be <highlight>accessed</highlight> by UNESCO managers and will stay in our database for six months.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你的申请将被联合国教科文组织的管理人员访问，并将在我们的数据库中保存六个月。

examination_example.sentence: We <highlight>accessed</highlight> the wall through the South Gate.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们通过南门进入城墙。

examination_example.sentence: Thus, the keyboard can determine people's identities, and by extension, whether they should be given <highlight>access</highlight> to the computer it's connected to.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 因此，该智能键盘可以确定人们的身份，来进一步决定是否允许他们访问其所连接的计算机。

examination_example.sentence: Enabling organizations and individuals to create digital humans themselves using <highlight>free-access</highlight> platforms they provide.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 使组织和个人能够使用他们提供的免费平台自己创造数字人类。

examination_example.sentence: All applicants must have a driver's license and <highlight>access</highlight> to a car.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 所有申请者必须有驾照和汽车。

examination_example.sentence: In a new civilization rich in machine intelligence, we have easy <highlight>access</highlight> to smart memory networks where information is stored.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在一个充满机器智能的新文明中，我们可以很容易地访问存储信息的智能存储网络。

examination_example.sentence: Another problem relates to the ease of <highlight>accessing</highlight> information.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 另一个问题与获取信息的便捷性有关。

examination_example.sentence: The ease of <highlight>accessing</highlight> information from the Internet.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 从互联网上获取信息的便利性。

sense_info_list.zh: 通道; 入径; 机会

examination_example.sentence: And as Internet <highlight>access</highlight> (通道) becomes available to even more people around the world, this growth won't stop anytime soon.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 随着世界各地越来越多的人能够使用互联网，这种增长不会很快停止。

examination_example.sentence: Nowadays, smart machines give us <highlight>access</highlight> to most human knowledge.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如今，智能机器给给我们机会接触大多数人类知识。

examination_example.sentence: He and his group, World <highlight>Access</highlight> for the Blind, teach others how to use sonar.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他和他的团队，世界盲人协会，教其他人如何使用声纳。

examination_example.sentence: We can have <highlight>access</highlight> to the most advanced equipment and experience the best teaching effects.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们可以使用最先进的设备，体验最好的教学效果。

examination_example.sentence: As the Internet grows more powerful, students can <highlight>access</highlight>(获得) knowledge easily.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 随着互联网越来越强大，学生可以很容易地获取知识。
